      "widgets_values": [
        "StarWalkway, korean couple walking slowly together through a surreal star light installation at night,\n\nThe background is completely and absolutely black: no environment, no ground, no sky, no depth, no gradients, no shadows, no reflections, no visible surfaces of any kind. Everything except the LED stars is swallowed by a pure black void.\n\nOnly floating star-shaped LED ornaments exist — pure white — suspended in infinite darkness at varying depths and heights, like a drifting constellation. Their light blooms into large soft overexposed halos with strong glow diffusion, cinematic bloom, and analog film halation, but does NOT illuminate the environment.\n\nThe stars softly flicker and drift, creating a surreal zero-gravity feeling.\n\nThe walkway is invisible. The surroundings do not exist. No ambient light whatsoever. No bounce light. No indirect lighting.\n\nA quiet, intimate, dreamlike, emotionally isolated atmosphere inside an infinite void.\n\nADDCOMM\n(masterpiece, best quality, highres, 35mm analog film, heavy film grain, extreme underexposure, cinematic contrast, strong bloom, glow diffusion, halation, light bleed, ethereal, surreal, minimalism, pitch black background, pure black void, zero ambient light, only point light sources visible)\n\nADDBASE\nA young handsome Korean man is mostly a dark silhouette, but NOT completely flat — \nvery subtle low-intensity front fill light reveals faint facial structure, nose bridge, and clothing folds.\n,slightly visible fabric texture.\nA clear luminous rim light outlines his entire silhouette with strong bloom and halation.\n\nADDCOL\nA young beautiful Korean woman is also mostly in shadow, but partially visible — \nsoft, minimal front lighting reveals gentle facial features.\nHer silhouette remains dominant, but not fully blacked out.\nA delicate glowing rim light traces her contour with soft diffusion and light bleed.\n\nBoth figures remain predominantly dark, with only 5~15% visibility in shadows, preserving silhouette dominance while allowing subtle human detail.",
        "Horizontal",
        "1,1",
